unction of $A$, which is similar as in the quantum kicked rotator, but\ndifferent from a mixed type billiard.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Apr 2021 17:02:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
