he Brody distribution with various values of the level repulsion\nexponent $\\beta$, its value depending on the strength of the localization of\nthe chaotic eigenstates. Consequently, the total spectrum is well described by\nthe Berry-Robnik-Brody (BRB) distribution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Apr 2021 18:08:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-03"}
