ieved a clustering accuracy of 79%, which is\nabout 5% higher than all existing baselines. These empirical results suggest\nthat DECAMP is a very effective method for unsupervised learning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 18 Apr 2021 22:02:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 02:42:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Apr 2021 14:32:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-27"}
