are important in providing microscopic mechanism in\nunderstanding the nonlocal rheologies and guide principles in developing\nconstitutive relations of real granular materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 05:00:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Apr 2021 12:07:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Oct 2021 14:43:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
