aring affordances of OSNs, information diffusion processes are also\nmodelled and taken explicitly into account. Altogether, the removal of\ngatekeeper nodes is further explored as a strategy to counteract unwanted data\ndissemination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 08:49:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 08:55:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-07"}
