mechanism involves exclusively hybridization between the low- and high-energy\nbands and this limits the computational efficiency gain of downfolded models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2021 11:05:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 May 2021 15:37:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2021 18:25:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
